{"tid":58570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰維斯正式加盟上海申花","createTime":"2016-12-29T02:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T04:24:23.000Z","uid":26467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f219d54942d63dbe1ddfee28f4c39c8bae50f0e9","tid":58570,"uid":26467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"中超球會上海綠地申花正式宣佈，效力阿甲小保加的泰維斯加盟。32歲的泰維斯將通過體檢後，到冲繩與球隊會合，他上周才舉行婚禮，正在烏拉圭度蜜月。泰維斯球員生涯也效力過韋斯咸、曼聯、曼城及祖雲達斯等，是一位速度型前鋒，在前方竄擾力甚強，而今次轉會費約1,100萬歐元（約8,900萬港元），為期兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161229&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56104790[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161229%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56104790%5B%2Furl&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=00a89f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161229%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56104790%5B%2Furl&h=68949e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161229&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56104790[/url</a>"},{"pid":"48f5c8575deab2d1f2fe858837891e306de0afa7","tid":58570,"uid":26467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmctZVx2fjEQV97A9yiUxUYqnUWczgF1rqgLo3GgfVZohY?filename=P086VYP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP086VYP.jpg&h=98eba12b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea005a8da3d8f3f873c4e55ceb2f69da8780d272","tid":58570,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1335cb0094dc405537e338899d9fe255c9ce748","tid":58570,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29